{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886520200,"sessionID":"ses_284ec6c0effeuVBVVdzk4kiXnu","part":{"id":"prt_d7b15cf00001XOt9uNyC0wAcN2","messageID":"msg_d7b13f1d8001Sxri0ohzumOCcN","sessionID":"ses_284ec6c0effeuVBVVdzk4kiXnu","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-f4924c0785e843768228a9db3d165c3d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md","content":"# AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) |\n| Module | `docker` |\n| Language | Dockerfile |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: WorkloadManager Dockerfile Foundation (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Create builder stage with golang:1.24-alpine base\n  - Purpose: Define builder stage for Go compilation\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"FROM golang:1.24-alpine AS builder\" docker/Dockerfile`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2**: Add go.mod/go.sum COPY and cache mount for module download\n  - Purpose: Optimize module download with BuildKit cache\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"RUN --mount=type=cache,target=/go/pkg/mod\" docker/Dockerfile`\n\n- [ ] **T1.3**: Add source COPY and CGO_ENABLED=0 environment\n  - Purpose: Prepare source for static compilation\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile`\n\n- [ ] **T1.4**: Add go build with ldflags optimization and build cache mount\n  - Purpose: Build optimized binary with stripped symbols\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"ldflags=\\\"-w -s\\\"\" docker/Dockerfile && grep \"go build\" docker/Dockerfile`\n\n- [ ] **T1.5**: Create runtime stage with alpine:3.19 base\n  - Purpose: Define minimal runtime base image\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"FROM alpine:3.19\" docker/Dockerfile`\n\n- [ ] **T1.6**: Add ca-certificates and tzdata packages\n  - Purpose: Install TLS certs and timezone data\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"apk add --no-cache ca-certificates tzdata\" docker/Dockerfile`\n\n- [ ] **T1.7**: Create non-root user apiserver (UID 1000)\n  - Purpose: Add security through non-root execution\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"adduser -D -u 1000 apiserver\" docker/Dockerfile`\n\n- [ ] **T1.8**: COPY binary from builder stage to runtime\n  - Purpose: Extract compiled binary from builder\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"COPY --from=builder\" docker/Dockerfile && grep \"workloadmanager\" docker/Dockerfile`\n\n- [ ] **T1.9**: Set USER 1000 and EXPOSE 8080\n  - Purpose: Configure security context and port\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"USER 1000\" docker/Dockerfile && grep \"EXPOSE 8080\" docker/Dockerfile`\n\n- [ ] **T1.10**: Set ENTRYPOINT for workloadmanager binary\n  - Purpose: Define container entrypoint\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"ENTRYPOINT \\[\\\"/app/bin/workloadmanager\\\"\\]\" docker/Dockerfile`\n\n### Phase 2: Router Dockerfile Foundation (ST-2)\n\n- [ ] **T2.1**: Create builder stage with golang:1.24-alpine base\n  - Purpose: Define builder stage for Go compilation\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `grep \"FROM golang:1.24-alpine AS builder\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2**: Add go.mod/go.sum COPY and cache mount for module download\n  - Purpose: Optimize module download with BuildKit cache\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `grep \"RUN --mount=type=cache,target=/go/pkg/mod\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n\n- [ ] **T2.3**: Add source COPY including client-go/\n  - Purpose: Include client-go module for router\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `grep \"COPY client-go/ client-go/\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n\n- [ ] **T2.4**: Add CGO_ENABLED=0 and go build with ldflags\n  - Purpose: Build optimized router binary\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile.router && grep \"./cmd/router\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n\n- [ ] **T2.5**: Create runtime stage with alpine:3.19 base\n  - Purpose: Define minimal runtime base image\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `grep \"FROM alpine:3.19\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n\n- [ ] **T2.6**: Add ca-certificates, tzdata, and non-root user router (UID 1000)\n  - Purpose: Install packages and create security user\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `grep \"adduser -D -u 1000 router\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n\n- [ ] **T2.7**: COPY router binary from builder and set USER 1000\n  - Purpose: Extract binary and configure security\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `grep \"/app/bin/router\" docker/Dockerfile.router && grep \"USER 1000\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n\n- [ ] **T2.8**: Set EXPOSE 8080 and ENTRYPOINT for router binary\n  - Purpose: Configure port and entrypoint\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `grep \"ENTRYPOINT \\[\\\"/app/bin/router\\\"\\]\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n\n### Phase 3: PicoD Dockerfile Foundation (ST-3)\n\n- [ ] **T3.1**: Create builder stage with golang:1.24 base (not Alpine)\n  - Purpose: Use standard golang image for Ubuntu runtime compatibility\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `grep \"FROM golang:1.24 AS builder\" docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n\n- [ ] **T3.2**: Add go.mod/go.sum COPY and go mod download (no cache mount)\n  - Purpose: Download modules without BuildKit cache for simplicity\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `grep \"go mod download\" docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n\n- [ ] **T3.3**: Add source COPY, CGO_ENABLED=0, and go build for picod\n  - Purpose: Build picod binary for sandbox management\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `grep \"./cmd/picod\" docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n\n- [ ] **T3.4**: Create runtime stage with ubuntu:24.04 base\n  - Purpose: Ubuntu base for Python3 sandbox support\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `grep \"FROM ubuntu:24.04\" docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n\n- [ ] **T3.5**: Install python3, python3-pip, ca-certificates packages\n  - Purpose: Install code execution dependencies\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `grep \"python3\" docker/Dockerfile.picod && grep \"apt-get install\" docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n\n- [ ] **T3.6**: COPY picod binary from builder (no USER directive - runs as root)\n  - Purpose: Extract binary with root privileges for sandbox management\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `grep \"COPY --from=builder\" docker/Dockerfile.picod && grep \"/app/bin/picod\" docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n\n- [ ] **T3.7**: Set EXPOSE 8080 and ENTRYPOINT for picod binary\n  - Purpose: Configure port and entrypoint\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `grep \"ENTRYPOINT \\[\\\"/app/bin/picod\\\"\\]\" docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n\n### Phase 4: Makefile Build Targets (ST-4)\n\n- [ ] **T4.1**: Add docker-build target for WorkloadManager\n  - Purpose: Add Makefile target for building workloadmanager image\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"docker-build:\" Makefile && grep \"docker/Dockerfile\" Makefile`\n\n- [ ] **T4.2**: Add docker-build-router target\n  - Purpose: Add Makefile target for building router image\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"docker-build-router:\" Makefile && grep \"Dockerfile.router\" Makefile`\n\n- [ ] **T4.3**: Add docker-build-picod target\n  - Purpose: Add Makefile target for building picod image\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"docker-build-picod:\" Makefile && grep \"Dockerfile.picod\" Makefile`\n\n- [ ] **T4.4**: Add docker-build-all aggregate target\n  - Purpose: Build all three images with single target\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"docker-build-all:\" Makefile`\n\n- [ ] **T4.5**: Add docker-buildx-push targets for multi-arch builds\n  - Purpose: Support linux/amd64,linux/arm64 multi-arch builds\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verification: `grep \"docker-buildx-push\" Makefile && grep \"linux/amd64,linux/arm64\" Makefile`\n\n### Phase 5: Dockerfile Syntax Validation (ST-5)\n\n- [ ] **T5.1**: Verify all three Dockerfiles exist\n  - Purpose: Confirm Dockerfile files created\n  - File: `docker/`\n  - Verification: `test -f docker/Dockerfile && test -f docker/Dockerfile.router && test -f docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n\n- [ ] **T5.2**: Verify workloadmanager has multi-stage structure\n  - Purpose: Confirm two-stage build pattern\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `grep -c \"FROM\" docker/Dockerfile | grep \"2\"`\n\n- [ ] **T5.3**: Verify router has multi-stage structure\n  - Purpose: Confirm two-stage build pattern\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `grep -c \"FROM\" docker/Dockerfile.router | grep \"2\"`\n\n- [ ] **T5.4**: Verify picod has multi-stage structure\n  - Purpose: Confirm two-stage build pattern\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `grep -c \"FROM\" docker/Dockerfile.picod | grep \"2\"`\n\n- [ ] **T5.5**: Verify Alpine Dockerfiles use golang:1.24-alpine builder\n  - Purpose: Confirm Alpine builder base for workloadmanager/router\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`, `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `grep \"golang:1.24-alpine\" docker/Dockerfile docker/Dockerfile.router`\n\n- [ ] **T5.6**: Verify Alpine runtime Dockerfiles have USER 1000\n  - Purpose: Confirm non-root user for workloadmanager/router\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`, `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `grep \"USER 1000\" docker/Dockerfile docker/Dockerfile.router`\n\n- [ ] **T5.7**: Verify picod runs as root (no USER directive)\n  - Purpose: Confirm root privileges for sandbox management\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `grep \"USER\" docker/Dockerfile.picod || echo \"OK\"`\n\n- [ ] **T5.8**: Verify all Dockerfiles have CGO_ENABLED=0\n  - Purpose: Confirm static compilation setting\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`, `docker/Dockerfile.router`, `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile docker/Dockerfile.router docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n\n- [ ] **T5.9**: Verify all Dockerfiles have ldflags=\"-w -s\" optimization\n  - Purpose: Confirm binary size optimization\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`, `docker/Dockerfile.router`, `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `grep \"ldflags\" docker/Dockerfile docker/Dockerfile.router docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n\n### Phase 6: Build Execution Tests (ST-6)\n\n- [ ] **T6.1**: Build workloadmanager image successfully\n  - Purpose: Verify workloadmanager builds without errors\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t agentcube-test-workloadmanager . && echo \"PASS\"`\n\n- [ ] **T6.2**: Build router image successfully\n  - Purpose: Verify router builds without errors\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-test-router . && echo \"PASS\"`\n\n- [ ] **T6.3**: Build picod image successfully\n  - Purpose: Verify picod builds without errors\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.picod -t agentcube-test-picod . && echo \"PASS\"`\n\n- [ ] **T6.4**: Verify workloadmanager image size <50MB\n  - Purpose: Confirm image meets size target\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `docker image inspect agentcube-test-workloadmanager --format='{{.Size}}' | awk '{if($1<50000000) print \"PASS\"; else print \"FAIL\"}'`\n\n- [ ] **T6.5**: Verify router image size <50MB\n  - Purpose: Confirm image meets size target\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `docker image inspect agentcube-test-router --format='{{.Size}}' | awk '{if($1<50000000) print \"PASS\"; else print \"FAIL\"}'`\n\n- [ ] **T6.6**: Verify picod image size <100MB\n  - Purpose: Confirm image meets size target (Ubuntu base larger)\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `docker image inspect agentcube-test-picod --format='{{.Size}}' | awk '{if($1<100000000) print \"PASS\"; else print \"FAIL\"}'`\n\n### Phase 7: Runtime Verification Tests (ST-7)\n\n- [ ] **T7.1**: Verify workloadmanager binary exists in runtime image\n  - Purpose: Confirm binary copied from builder\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-workloadmanager test -f /app/bin/workloadmanager`\n\n- [ ] **T7.2**: Verify router binary exists in runtime image\n  - Purpose: Confirm binary copied from builder\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-router test -f /app/bin/router`\n\n- [ ] **T7.3**: Verify picod binary exists in runtime image\n  - Purpose: Confirm binary copied from builder\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-picod test -f /app/bin/picod`\n\n- [ ] **T7.4**: Verify workloadmanager runs as UID 1000\n  - Purpose: Confirm non-root security context\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-workloadmanager id -u | grep \"1000\"`\n\n- [ ] **T7.5**: Verify router runs as UID 1000\n  - Purpose: Confirm non-root security context\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-router id -u | grep \"1000\"`\n\n- [ ] **T7.6**: Verify picod runs as root (UID 0)\n  - Purpose: Confirm root privileges for sandbox management\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-picod id -u | grep \"0\"`\n\n- [ ] **T7.7**: Verify workloadmanager has no Go toolchain\n  - Purpose: Confirm minimal runtime (no build tools)\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-workloadmanager which go 2>&1 | grep -v \"/usr\" || echo \"PASS\"`\n\n- [ ] **T7.8**: Verify workloadmanager has no Go source files\n  - Purpose: Confirm source not leaked to runtime\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-workloadmanager find /app -name \"*.go\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l | grep \"0\"`\n\n- [ ] **T7.9**: Verify picod has python3 installed\n  - Purpose: Confirm code execution dependency\n  - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-picod which python3`\n\n### Phase 8: Makefile Integration Tests (ST-8)\n\n- [ ] **T8.1**: Run make docker-build successfully\n  - Purpose: Verify Makefile target works\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verification: `make docker-build IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test`\n\n- [ ] **T8.2**: Run make docker-build-router successfully\n  - Purpose: Verify Makefile target works\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verification: `make docker-build-router IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test`\n\n- [ ] **T8.3**: Run make docker-build-picod successfully\n  - Purpose: Verify Makefile target works\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verification: `make docker-build-picod IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test`\n\n- [ ] **T8.4**: Run make docker-build-all successfully\n  - Purpose: Verify aggregate target builds all images\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verification: `make docker-build-all IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test`\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nPhase 1 (WorkloadManager Dockerfile) ───────────────────────────────────────────\nT1.1 (builder FROM) ──┬── T1.2 (go mod download + cache)\n                      ├── T1.3 (COPY source + CGO_ENABLED)\n                      ├── T1.4 (go build + ldflags)\n                      ├── T1.5 (runtime FROM alpine)\n                      ├── T1.6 (apk packages)\n                      ├── T1.7 (adduser apiserver)\n                      ├── T1.8 (COPY --from=builder)\n                      ├── T1.9 (USER + EXPOSE)\n                      └── T1.10 (ENTRYPOINT)\n\nPhase 2 (Router Dockerfile) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT2.1 (builder FROM) ──┬── T2.2 (go mod download + cache)\n                      ├── T2.3 (COPY client-go/)\n                      ├── T2.4 (CGO + go build)\n                      ├── T2.5 (runtime FROM alpine)\n                      ├── T2.6 (apk + adduser router)\n                      ├── T2.7 (COPY --from=builder + USER)\n                      └── T2.8 (EXPOSE + ENTRYPOINT)\n\nPhase 3 (PicoD Dockerfile) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT3.1 (builder FROM golang) ──┬── T3.2 (go mod download)\n                             ├── T3.3 (CGO + go build)\n                             ├── T3.4 (runtime FROM ubuntu)\n                             ├── T3.5 (apt-get python3)\n                             ├── T3.6 (COPY --from=builder)\n                             └── T3.7 (EXPOSE + ENTRYPOINT)\n\nPhase 4 (Makefile Targets) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT1.1-T1.10 ──┬── T4.1 (docker-build)\nT2.1-T2.8 ───┬── T4.2 (docker-build-router)\nT3.1-T3.7 ───┬── T4.3 (docker-build-picod)\n             ├── T4.4 (docker-build-all)\n             └── T4.5 (docker-buildx-push)\n\nPhase 5 (Syntax Validation) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT1.1-T4.5 ──┬── T5.1-T5.9 (syntax checks)\n\nPhase 6 (Build Execution) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT5.1-T5.9 ──┬── T6.1-T6.3 (build tests)\n            ├── T6.4-T6.6 (size verification)\n\nPhase 7 (Runtime Verification) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT6.1-T6.6 ──┬── T7.1-T7.9 (runtime tests)\n\nPhase 8 (Makefile Integration) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT4.1-T4.5 ──┬── T8.1-T8.4 (make target tests)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n| Task Phase | Verification Command |\n|------------|----------------------|\n| Phase 1 | `grep -c \"FROM\" docker/Dockerfile | grep \"2\"` |\n| Phase 2 | `grep -c \"FROM\" docker/Dockerfile.router | grep \"2\"` |\n| Phase 3 | `grep -c \"FROM\" docker/Dockerfile.picod | grep \"2\"` |\n| Phase 4 | `grep \"docker-build-all:\" Makefile` |\n| Phase 5 | `grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile docker/Dockerfile.router docker/Dockerfile.picod` |\n| Phase 6 | `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t test-workloadmanager . && docker image inspect test-workloadmanager --format='{{.Size}}'` |\n| Phase 7 | `docker run --rm test-workloadmanager id -u | grep \"1000\"` |\n| Phase 8 | `make docker-build-all IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test` |\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] WorkloadManager Dockerfile has 2-stage build structure\n- [ ] Router Dockerfile has 2-stage build structure\n- [ ] PicoD Dockerfile has 2-stage build structure\n- [ ] WorkloadManager uses golang:1.24-alpine builder + alpine:3.19 runtime\n- [ ] Router uses golang:1.24-alpine builder + alpine:3.19 runtime\n- [ ] PicoD uses golang:1.24 builder + ubuntu:24.04 runtime\n- [ ] WorkloadManager runs as UID 1000 (non-root)\n- [ ] Router runs as UID 1000 (non-root)\n- [ ] PicoD runs as root (UID 0)\n- [ ] All Dockerfiles have CGO_ENABLED=0\n- [ ] All Dockerfiles have ldflags=\"-w -s\" optimization\n- [ ] WorkloadManager/Router use BuildKit cache mounts for go mod/go build\n- [ ] Router Dockerfile includes client-go/ COPY\n- [ ] PicoD Dockerfile installs python3, python3-pip\n- [ ] WorkloadManager image size <50MB\n- [ ] Router image size <50MB\n- [ ] PicoD image size <100MB\n- [ ] Makefile has docker-build target\n- [ ] Makefile has docker-build-router target\n- [ ] Makefile has docker-build-picod target\n- [ ] Makefile has docker-build-all target\n- [ ] Makefile has docker-buildx-push targets for multi-arch\n- [ ] Runtime images have no Go toolchain\n- [ ] Runtime images have no Go source files\n- [ ] All images build successfully with make docker-build-all\n\n---\n\n## File Changes Summary\n\n| File | Action | Lines | Description |\n|------|--------|-------|-------------|\n| `docker/Dockerfile` | Create | 25 | WorkloadManager multi-stage build (builder → runtime) |\n| `docker/Dockerfile.router` | Create | 30 | Router multi-stage build (builder → runtime with client-go) |\n| `docker/Dockerfile.picod` | Create | 25 | PicoD multi-stage build (builder → Ubuntu runtime) |\n| `Makefile` | Modify | 35 | Add docker-build, docker-build-router, docker-build-picod, docker-build-all, docker-buildx-push targets |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### Multi-Stage Build Pattern\n\n```dockerfile\n# Stage 1: Builder\nFROM golang:1.24-alpine AS builder\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY go.mod go.sum ./\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/go/pkg/mod go mod download\nCOPY . .\nENV CGO_ENABLED=0\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.cache/go-build \\\n    go build -ldflags=\"-w -s\" -o /app/bin/<binary> ./cmd/<module>\n\n# Stage 2: Runtime\nFROM alpine:3.19\nRUN apk add --no-cache ca-certificates tzdata\nRUN adduser -D -u 1000 <user>\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY --from=builder /app/bin/<binary> /app/bin/<binary>\nUSER 1000\nEXPOSE 8080\nENTRYPOINT [\" /app/bin/<binary>\"]\n```\n\n### BuildKit Cache Optimization\n\n| Cache Mount | Target | Purpose |\n|-------------|--------|---------|\n| `/go/pkg/mod` | Module cache | Persist module downloads across builds |\n| `/root/.cache/go-build` | Build cache | Cache compiled artifacts |\n\n### Binary Size Optimization Flags\n\n| Flag | Effect |\n|------|--------|\n| `-w` | Strip DWARF debug information |\n| `-s` | Strip symbol table |\n| `CGO_ENABLED=0` | Static-like compilation |\n\n### User Security Context\n\n| Image | User | Reason |\n|-------|------|--------|\n| WorkloadManager | UID 1000 | Non-root for security |\n| Router | UID 1000 | Non-root for security |\n| PicoD | root (UID 0) | Sandbox pod management requires elevated privileges |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: WorkloadManager Dockerfile | T1.1-T1.10 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 2: Router Dockerfile | T2.1-T2.8 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 3: PicoD Dockerfile | T3.1-T3.7 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 4: Makefile Targets | T4.1-T4.5 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 5: Syntax Validation | T5.1-T5.9 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 6: Build Execution | T6.1-T6.6 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 7: Runtime Verification | T7.1-T7.9 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 8: Makefile Integration | T8.1-T8.4 | Pending | 0% |\n\n**Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/46 tasks)**\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Design: `changes/AR-032/design.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n- Proposal: `changes/AR-032/proposal.md`\n- Docker multi-stage builds: https://docs.docker.com/build/building/multi-stage/\n- BuildKit cache mounts: https://docs.docker.com/build/buildkit/#cache-mounts\n- Go cross-compilation: https://go.dev/doc/install/source#environment"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775886520153,"end":1775886520195}}}}
